title: Bump zipp from 3.0.0 to 3.1.0
body:
Bumps [zipp](https://github.com/jaraco/zipp) from 3.0.0 to 3.1.0.
Changelog

Sourced from zipp's changelog.

v3.1.0

#47: .open now raises FileNotFoundError and IsADirectoryError when appropriate.
